# {project_name} -- CMA agent notes

CMA-shaped project notes. Generated by `swanlake init project --type cma`.

## Hard rules

1. **No AI attribution anywhere.** Strip from any default template that
   tries to inject it.
2. **No real-shaped canary literals in tracked files.** They live only
   in the operator's local registry which MUST be gitignored.
3. **All commits must be signed AND DCO-signed-off.** Use
   `git commit -S --signoff`. Never `--no-verify`.

